{"tid":1567750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家，我地唔係動員力低，我地係自發性強","createTime":"2019-09-14T07:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T07:16:01.000Z","uid":262084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a1edaa9a7b2b0cdf374546677875bf26e1a55618","tid":1567750,"uid":262084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:10:31.000Z","msg":"我地跟本唔需要好似佢地咁組隊去做野，我地每人都係自發去做野。<br />\n<br />\n破壞左既連儂牆唔需要半日就可以收復返。<br />\n<br />\n我地依家係要同對家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鬥長命！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講人數一定係我地多，佢動員出來拆我地就貼，講毅力佢地一定唔夠我地多，同埋佢地人少要付出既勞力一定比我地多<br />\n<br />\n我地依家係要堅持貼到十一以後<br />\n<br />\n我地唔需要做強者，相返我地要做弱者，顯示佢地比我地做成更加大既破壞，無差別打人，要警察冇得辨駁佢地既偏頗"},{"pid":"b7ee642903469c95748ef66605af5b46af7b00f4","tid":1567750,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}